ZH: 这墙是用砖头砌的。
EN: This wall is built with bricks.

ZH: 他用砖头砌了一座小房子。
EN: He built a small house with bricks.

ZH: 街道是由灰色的砖头铺成的。
EN: The street is paved with grey bricks.

ZH: 建筑工人们在搬运砖头。
EN: Construction workers are moving bricks.

ZH: 这块砖头很重。
EN: This brick is very heavy.

ZH: 请小心踩到这些砖头。
EN: Please be careful not to step on these bricks.

ZH: 孩子们在玩扔砖头的游戏。
EN: The children are playing a game of throwing bricks.

ZH: 这些砖头是用回收材料制成的。
EN: These bricks are made from recycled materials.

ZH: 在乡村，房屋多用砖头建造。
EN: In the countryside, houses are mostly built with bricks.

ZH: 这个人正在把桶里的砖头搬上楼。
EN: The person is carrying the bricks from the bucket upstairs.

ZH: 工匠正在疏通炉子中的砖头。
EN: The craftsman is cleaning the bricks in the furnace.

ZH: 砖头是一种古老的建筑材料。
EN: Bricks are an ancient building material.

ZH: 我们把泥巴做成砖头。
EN: We make bricks out of mud.

ZH: 这里有些砖头掉了。
EN: Some bricks have fallen off here.

ZH: 这些砖头很耐用。
EN: These bricks are very durable.

ZH: 他们用砖头垫高了路缘。
EN: They raised the curb with bricks.

ZH: 你可以把这些砖头拿出去。
EN: You can take these bricks out.

ZH: 这个书架是用砖头和木板做成的。
EN: This bookshelf is made of bricks and wooden boards.

ZH: 我在车库找到一块旧砖头。
EN: I found an old brick in the garage.

ZH: 这些建筑是用粉红色的砖头建造的。
EN: These buildings are constructed with pink bricks.
